data.description: Great opportunity for a first time homebuyer or investor -Located in the Stonehurst section of Upper Darby.  Large front patio and rear deck to enjoy those beautiful Spring/Summer/Fall days. The first floor features a large formal living room, formal dining room, and kitchen with direct access to rear deck. The second floor has two good sized bedrooms and a full hall bath.  The basement is finished, with laundry facilities, and exit door to the back of the house.  The finished basement can be used as a play area, office or extra bedroom.  All this plus a one car garage. The home also has a newer water heater and windows were installed in 2008. Schedule you're showing today!
